The thing that I think is interesting about this series is the fact that no one is in the wrong here. The uncle and the sister is just basically in a very "questionable" relationship (like many other hentai about incest) and their kinkiness is involving the brother. Some people might think the couple is in the wrong, however, in my perspective, this is just how one-sided love in real life exaggerated. The person he likes doesn't like him back and chooses to be with another man. Due to the relationship they are having (in this case brother-sister, but in other cases it can be schoolmates or co-workers), he is forced to endure their flirty behaviors through a long time. It is painful to watch but... that's just how realistic your heart reacts to that. It is because you sympathize with the emotions of the brother who has no choice but to cope with everything that is happening and often being dragged into their love life. Yet, he can't blame anyone because no one is at fault.
